_sText:
I built this map in exactly 1 month and still it is a respectably long and well built map, vaguely "inspired" by trikz_noflash i guess with the similar textures.

- 15 levels

- 4 level bonus provided by george

- Lj room from 240 - 269

- Short bhop bonus

The map should be entirely bug free but if you do happen to see any bug please report it to me.

Anyone that participated in the beta yesterday will have to redownload map or your map will differ.

I had alot of fun making this map and i hope you enjoy playing it.
